description.narrative:
The objectives of the programme include 
1) Youth have access to youth friendly microfinance schemes, quality and market driven vocational and technical training, life skills and enterprise development trainings; 
2) Youth, particularly young women, from the targeted areas increase their levels of economic work (self or paid employment) in traditional and non-traditional occupations;
3) Local communities and parents increasingly recognize and encourage youth, particularly young women, to become socially and economically active members of society.
